            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1245474</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
<p>日本漫畫家諫山創的人氣漫畫作品《進擊的巨人》連載 12 年終於迎來結局，早前動畫版亦已正式播映完畢，相信各位粉絲都大感不捨，。如果你是巨人粉絲的話，就不容錯過小編今日介紹的《進擊的巨人》機械鍵盤套裝。全新機械鍵盤套裝即日起接受預訂，實物將於香港動漫電玩節 2024 〈動漫聯動〉攤位展出、公開發售，預訂了的朋友也可進場取貨。現在就讓小編開箱先睹為快，和大家看看這套機械鍵盤。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245806" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09708-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09708-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09708.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《進擊的巨人》機械鍵盤由台灣機械鍵盤品牌 Ducky 製造，採用 Ducky One 2 RGB 108 鍵規格，搭載 PBT 熱昇華鍵帽和德國 Cherry MX 機械茶軸，更有多達 8 種背光模式，而且配有 3 段式調整高度腳架，方便用家調節至適合自己的高度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245808" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09709-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09709-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09709.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245897" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09739-2-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09739-2-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09739-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 搭載德國 Cherry MX 機械茶軸</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245876" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09734-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09734-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09734.jpg