"text-align: center;">▲鍵帽上印有多個重要角色</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245877" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09737-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09737-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09737.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲鍵帽上印有多個重要角色</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245858" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09717-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09717-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09717.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲鍵盤底部印有角色剪影</p><p>鍵盤配備 4 款印有重要場面的可替換空白鍵，以及 3 道城牆紋章設計的普通按鍵。除此之外，還有最終季動畫主視覺圖的長滑鼠墊及明信片組。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245860" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09725-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09725-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09725.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可替換空白鍵 + 普通按鍵</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245862" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09707-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09707-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09707.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲進擊