            <title>議員倡香港發展空中的士載客觀光    「可參考中國及歐美推動低空經濟」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/04/air-taxi-2/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=air-taxi-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/04/air-taxi-2/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 07:20:22 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[低空經濟]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[劉業強]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[吳永嘉]]>
